@startuml
!theme plain
title 06. OpenZFS Media Layout
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Coherence write policy" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "DPU NVMe-oF" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "OpenZFS zpool" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Mirrored NAND vdevs" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Scrub/resilver" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : durable writes
N2 --> N3 : namespace I/O
N3 --> N4 : checksummed blocks
N4 --> N5 : mirror replication

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
